Name:           perl-Flickr-Upload
Version:        1.32
Release:        10%{?dist}
Summary:        Flickr.com upload module and script
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Group:          Development/Libraries
URL:            http://search.cpan.org/dist/Flickr-Upload/
